{"tid":2296481,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登失態喝斥CBS記者｢怎麼就你經常大叫提問?｣ 未答問題即驅離對方","createTime":"2020-11-22T13:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T15:39:24.000Z","uid":75656,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"74769361d28cc3f6b58d994ca538f4ab9cb933ec","tid":2296481,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:34:51.000Z","msg":"拜登周五與副手賀錦麗（Kamala Harris）在德拉瓦州威明頓（Wilmington）巿與眾議院議長裴洛西（Nancy Pelosi）和參院少數黨領袖舒默（Chuck Schumer）會面。<br />\n<br />\n會面結束之際，工作人員要求在場記者離開，這時艾利克森大聲向拜登提問：「拜登先生，武漢肺炎工作小組說已可安全讓學生回去上課，你會鼓勵（教師）工會加強合作，讓孩子回到教室嗎？」拜登沒有回應，反斥責：「怎麼就你經常大喊提問 ？」<br />\n<br />\n美國廣播公司（ABC）記者史特金（Will Steakin）指：「艾利克森做得好，（拜登說他）『大喊』問題也太好笑」。《國會山莊報》記者康查（Joe Concha）嘲諷：「大喊問題未來將被視為不尊重、不良的行為」。<br />\n<br />\n獨立記者吉拉尼（Zaid Jilani）更表示，艾利克森是「想做新聞」，「<span class=\"red\">其他跑拜登線的記者大多只是速記員</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n艾利克森同事、CBS白宮記者芮德（Paula Reid）也寫道：「拜登問了好問題，為甚麼艾利克森是其中唯一提問的人？停課、疫苗、振興方案&mdash;&mdash;有很多重要問題應該問裴洛西和拜登」。<br />\n<br />\n拜登與艾利克森並非首次「交手」，上月艾利克森曾要求拜登回應涉及次子杭特的醜聞時，拜登顯得不滿，「我就知道你會問，我沒有回應，這又是一種抹黑行為，切合你的口味，這是你總會問的問題」。<span class=\"red\">艾利克森是少數曾就此事詢問拜登的主流媒體記者</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201122/5BHGKGVJPZFYVMPCIFKOK4MH4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201122%2F5BHGKGVJPZFYVMPCIFKOK4MH4Q%2F&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=3e394c62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201122%2F5BHGKGVJPZFYVMPCIFKOK4MH4Q%2F&h=7927833c\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201122/5BHGKGVJPZFYVMPCIFKOK4MH4Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/BoKnowsNews/status/1329895714973999109?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBoKnowsNews%2Fstatus%2F1329895714973999109%3Fs%3D20&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=58664dd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBoKnowsNews%2Fstatus%2F1329895714973999109%3Fs%3D20&h=c2086622\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/BoKnowsNews/status/1329895714973999109?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sNuQJFr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsNuQJFr.jpg&h=4b673054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個記者遲下會唔會被清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06e10bcce547ddefc7a8f8dd28b20e4a755a130","tid":2296481,"uid":48222,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:36:50.000Z","msg":"左膠又睇唔到，成日話侵侵犯新聞自由，china joe咪一鳩樣"},{"pid":"ec396ffd1e34792abe0c4fb8e80d29b2c141c34b","tid":2296481,"uid":37869,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f06e10bcce547ddefc7a8f8dd28b20e4a755a130","tid":2296481,"uid":48222,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:36:50.000Z","msg":"左膠又睇唔到，成日話侵侵犯新聞自由，china joe咪一鳩樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:38:30.000Z","msg":"想問下侵侵點侵犯新聞自由？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ddb4ef050504f8d21fbb3f5b3e85e2125dca2c","tid":2296481,"uid":48222,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"ec396ffd1e34792abe0c4fb8e80d29b2c141c34b","tid":2296481,"uid":37869,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f06e10bcce547ddefc7a8f8dd28b20e4a755a130","tid":2296481,"uid":48222,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:36:50.000Z","msg":"左膠又睇唔到，成日話侵侵犯新聞自由，china joe咪一鳩樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:38:30.000Z","msg":"想問下侵侵點侵犯新聞自由？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:39:19.000Z","msg":"話佢話人fake news同驅逐白宮妓者嘛"},{"pid":"1aaa0514863afbbd45653ab1450c855dbaf72be0","tid":2296481,"uid":4783,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:41:39.000Z","msg":"原來記者問問題都唔撚得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class